---
title: Chermoula Roasted Cauliflower with Garlicky Beans, Caramelised Onion Bulgur and Herby Drizzle
description: We love a good Chermoula Roasted Cauliflower and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chermoula-roasted-cauliflower-ca212ba5-40ccfa61.jpg
